00:34:03.670 --> 00:34:06.430
So yeah, I want to
be clear on this,

00:34:06.430 --> 00:34:09.090
that what happens
with crime and danger

00:34:09.090 --> 00:34:11.610
in the United States
between 1966 and 1993

00:34:11.610 --> 00:34:14.763
isn't some fiction.

00:34:14.763 --> 00:34:17.429
When I started commuting down to
Manhattan from the Bronx, where

00:34:17.429 --> 00:34:20.550
I grew up, to go to a magnet
school in the Upper East Side

00:34:20.550 --> 00:34:23.940
in 1992, there was 2,300
murders in New York City.

00:34:23.940 --> 00:34:26.739
